cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use OCTALUME in your research or product, please cite it as below."
title: "OCTALUME: AI-Native Enterprise SDLC Framework with Quality Gates and Multi-Agent Orchestration"
abstract: >-
  OCTALUME is an open-source, AI-native software development lifecycle
  framework that drives projects through 8 sequential phases with
  machine-checkable quality gates, 9 specialized AI agents, and built-in
  compliance scanners for HIPAA, SOC 2, PCI DSS, and GDPR. It exposes 30+
  tools via the Model Context Protocol (MCP) for direct integration with
  Claude Code and other agentic IDEs.
